  "instructions": [
    "Boil the cassava peeled and quartered in salted water until tender, about 20 minutes.",
    "Drain the cassava and mash it with a fork until smooth.",
    "In a food processor, combine the mashed cassava, basil, pine nuts, parmesan, and garlic.",
    "Pulse until a coarse paste forms, then add the olive oil and lemon juice in a steady stream.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Transfer the pesto to a shallow scallop shell for serving.",
    "Serve immediately, or refrigerate for up to 48 hours.",
